:'''Bronya:''' Before the Eternal Freeze? I do know about it, but I can't recite it all by memory.
:'''Bronya:''' If you are really interested, you should look on the shelf over there for a set of books called ''Belobog Chronicles''. They might be helpful references.
:'''Bronya:''' What got you suddenly interested in researching that history anyway? Did something happen?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Long story. It all started with an ad...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm on a research mission for the Express' data bank.
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201340341-->
:'''Bronya:''' I see...
:'''Bronya:''' ...Oh. What was that sound?
<pre>{
	"$type": "RPG.GameCore.PlayMessage",
	"MessageSectionID": 1112800
}</pre>
:'''Bronya:''' Pfft... I totally get it now.
:'''Bronya:''' That ''Chronicle'' is on the bookshelf. Feel free to have a look. If you can't find it, just let me know. I'll help you look.
:'''Bronya:''' The name Interastral Peace Appliances... does seem to ring a bell.
:'''Bronya:''' Interastral Peace Appliances... Interastral Peace...
:'''Bronya:''' Interastral Peace Corporation... I've read about it before in the Guardians' history textbook. I think it's some kind of interstellar organization that has massive influences all over the cosmos. It has something to do with Preservation...
:'''Bronya:''' Oh... never mind. They're all followers of the Amber Lord, but they probably have nothing to do with Belobog. So I need not worry about them for now.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Not necessarily.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201340350-->
::'''Bronya:''' Hmmm... maybe you're right. But I still believe they might be a net positive for Belobog if there comes a time when we do make contact with them in the future.
::'''Bronya:''' Alright. Go and find the book you need. Just let me know if you need any help.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll go look for the records then. Thank you.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201340353-->
::'''Bronya:''' You're welcome. I hope Qlipoth Fort's book collection will be of use to you.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_201150108-->
:'''Bronya:''' Of course, I do, (Trailblazer). I've always benefited lots from our discussions.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_501029101_15-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501029101_15-->
:{{DIcon|Talk}} How does it feel to be the Supreme Guardian?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029107-->
::'''Bronya:''' For me, it's just a title and nothing more. I'll still stick to doing the right thing with or without this title.
::'''Bronya:''' ...But not from the point of view of the people. For them, the Supreme Guardian is a powerful symbol &mdash; not just of the city's leadership, but also of a future with hope.
::'''Bronya:''' So I have to re-examine my thinking more critically. I have to always bear in mind that every decision I make could affect the lives of thousands of people...
::'''Bronya:''' It's a heavy load to bear. To be honest, I don't even know if I can do it. But I'm lucky &mdash; because I don't have to go through it all alone.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} What plans do you have next?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029112-->
::'''Bronya:''' The number one priority is to revitalize Belobog... Ah, it still sounds so vague, doesn't it?
::'''Bronya:''' As for specific actions, I think the number one priority is to reorganize the economy of Belobog.
::'''Bronya:''' The blockade has had a huge impact on the Overworld and Underworld economies. Right now, ordinary miners in the Underworld can't bear the high cost of living in the Administrative District.
::'''Bronya:''' If things don't get better, then you can forget about reintegrating the Overworld and the Underworld. I've booked meetings with several of the finance ministers to try to hammer out a basic direction for reforms.
::'''Bronya:''' &mdash; Of course, this is only the first step in a great revitalization plan. I hope it will be a strong start.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} About Cocolia...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029118-->
::'''Bronya:''' ...Keep your voice down, (Trailblazer).
::'''Bronya:''' As for Mom... All I can do is keep myself from remembering how she looked before she passed.
::'''Bronya:''' (Trailblazer), no matter what she might look like to you, Madam Cocolia was my only living family. Everything that has made me into the person I am... I owe it to her teachings.
::'''Bronya:''' I don't know when she started going astray, but this whole time, all she's ever done has been to shower me with love... And I don't think that's the Stellaron's influence.
::'''Bronya:''' Honestly speaking, the thought of not seeing her again... always wells me up with tears. Yet, now is not the time for me to show my vulnerable side.
::'''Bronya:''' So, let's talk about something else, (Trailblazer).
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Is Seele here?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029123-->
::'''Bronya:''' She wants to get stuck into some material change, rather than stick around in this lifeless office. She was always thinking about the Underworld. You can't stop someone like that from leaving.
::'''Bronya:''' Seele is a doer. She can't do what she does best at the negotiation table. She knows where her strengths lie... And as a friend and fellow fighter, I support her choice.
::'''Bronya:''' Besides, if I send a signal asking for her help... I know she'll return to me. And that's all I need.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} Thanks for your time, Bronya.
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501029101_12-->
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:'''Bronya:''' You're still here, (Trailblazer).
:'''Bronya:''' Despite Belobog being in a terrible state these days... You can always find its charming side, if only you look carefully enough.
:'''Bronya:''' I trust you have a meticulous eye for beauty, Trailblazer. I hope you have a great time in Belobog.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:'''Bronya:''' So long, (Trailblazer). I wish you all the best on your journey.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 90000037: Config/Level/NPC/W1/NPC_DefaultStory_501029101.json-->
