::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_501029103_12-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501029103_12-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What do you think about Topaz?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029143-->
:::'''Bronya:''' Miss Topaz... She is very complex.
:::'''Bronya:''' From the letter she gave me, I could sense her sincerity. Yet she would also withhold important information from me, and coerce and manipulate us into doing what she desires.
:::'''Bronya:''' However, I can feel that she is sincerely working for the future of this planet from the bottom of her heart, even if not everyone can accept her methods.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} She is very calculated.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029147-->
::::'''Bronya:''' You're right. It's a relief that she is on our side... I guess this is what you'd call a blessing in disguise, right? Though Belobog experienced a great trial, it also gained a powerful ally because of it.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501029151-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029151-->
::::'''Bronya:''' My wish is that this will make the IPC abandon their idea of interfering with Jarilo-VI. I hope Miss Topaz's promise carries enough weight...
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} She is a trustworthy person.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029149-->
::::'''Bronya:''' This is something we agree on. Though the power that she represents and the calculated schemes that she has displayed have caused us to remain guarded.
::::'''Bronya:''' It's a relief that she is on our side now... I guess this is what you'd call a blessing in disguise, right? Though Belobog experienced a great trial, it also gained a powerful ally because of it.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501029151-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029151-->
::::'''Bronya:''' My wish is that this will make the IPC abandon their idea of interfering with Jarilo-VI. I hope Miss Topaz's promise carries enough weight...
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} You almost signed the contract back then.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029153-->
:::'''Bronya:''' That's right... At that moment, I was on the verge of breaking down. Fortunately, Miss Himeko appeared in time and explained the whole picture.
:::'''Bronya:''' I wonder why Topaz didn't mention the numbers and probability in her letter... Was she confident enough in herself? Or did she deliberately hide them from me?
:::'''Bronya:''' ...Well, that's no longer important. What I need to reflect on is how I felt at that moment, I almost caved to the pressure... At that moment, all I wanted was to escape my responsibilities, once and for all.
:::'''Bronya:''' If things had not turned around, I may have betrayed the trust of all our citizens... and Seele's, too. I must learn from this lesson and continue to grow. My will must be stronger!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} There are many IPC people in the city.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029158-->
:::'''Bronya:''' Indeed, I permitted them to station in Belobog.
:::'''Bronya:''' Those that are stationed here are all Topaz's most trusted employees. It seems they call this place an "Exo-Technical Support Dispatch Zone."
:::'''Bronya:''' Whatever the case, we can definitely make use of the IPC's technology. If they can know their place and assist the citizens in their work, Belobog may even complete this "tech-leap" they speak of within a generation...
:::'''Bronya:''' Can you imagine, (Trailblazer)? There may come a day &mdash; once I step down from my role as Supreme Guardian &mdash; that we could really set out to travel together. This is no longer just a pipe dream.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the Engine of Creation and Pillars of Creation...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029163-->
:::'''Bronya:''' When you went in search of Topaz, I immediately made an appeal to the people on the Belobog city radio.
:::'''Bronya:''' I told the citizens everything behind the events surrounding the IPC, and urged them to pick up their tools and join the Silvermane guards northward, to direct their efforts toward the rebuilding of the Engine of Creation.
:::'''Bronya:''' And you all saw the outcome. The citizens of Belobog &mdash; regardless of background and status, both Underworlder and Overworlder &mdash; have all come together to contribute to maintaining the freedom and autonomy of this world.
:::'''Bronya:''' I'm so happy, (Trailblazer)... I no longer have to concoct a lie this time. I don't have to sacrifice my sincerity for the sake of stability.
:::'''Bronya:''' Perhaps, one day... people will also be able to calmly accept "that truth."
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} Thanks for your time, Bronya.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::'''Bronya:''' So long, (Trailblazer). I wish you all the best on your journey.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
